---
title: Caramelized BBQ Chicken Breasts with Succotash and Roasted Potatoes
description: The key to sticky sweet chicken is BBQ sauce that caramelizes perfectly under the broiler! Roasted potatoes and succotash turn this meal into a southern-inspired delight!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/poitrines-de-poulet-bbq-caramelisees-5d33cc06.jpg
